title: FIP-016 GDN Treasury Vault Purchase
body:
As according to last week’s Designer Spotlight Snapshot Paola was ranked as the highest voted designer.

The Designer Weekly spotlight activities will begin from Monday and take place over the course of the week.

One of these activities includes the GDN Treasury purchasing one of the NFTs from spotlighted designer from the DIGITALAX fashion marketplace and holding this in the GDN Treasury Vault. The following are the live listed NFTs by Paola on the marketplace;

1. Stella (https://fashion.digitalax.xyz/product/358/2/0/)
2. Transition through Emotion (https://fashion.digitalax.xyz/product/630/1/0/)
3. DeFi Fashion (https://fashion.digitalax.xyz/product/551/3/0/)

Note: The DIGITALAX DAO will also be voting on which item from Paola's collection on the marketplace to purchase for the DIGITALAX Treasury vault. If the DIGITALAX voters and GDN voters rank highest the same NFT across both proposals, then the DIGITALAX vote will get priority and the GDN DAO will go with the second highest chosen option.
